<h3>Conference Highlights: Friday, 20 September 2013</h3>

<!--p>Information will be added as it becomes available.</p-->

                              
<h4>57th Annual Session of IAEA General Conference Concludes</h4>
<br />
<p><img src="/newscenter/images/gc57d_150x100.jpg" alt="General Conference Ends" class="img-float-left" />The 57th annual session of the <em>IAEA General Conference</em> concluded today in Vienna. More than 3&nbsp;000 delegates from 159 IAEA Member States, international organizations, NGO's and the media attended the event held at the Austria Center, Vienna from 16-20 September 2013. The full texts of adopted resolutions will be posted in due course on the IAEA website. <a href="/newscenter/news/2013/gc57ends.html">More &rarr;</a> :: <a href="/newscenter/statements/2013/amsp2013n18.html">Director General Statement to Conference</a> &rarr;</a> :: <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/iaea_imagebank/collections/72157635569932382/">Photo Gallery &rarr;</a></p>


