<h4>Regulatory Cooperation Forum</h4>
<br />
<p><img src="/About/Policy/GC/GC57/images/rcf200913_150x100.jpg" alt="RCF" class="img-float-left" />The Regulatory Cooperation Forum (RCF) of the IAEA held a side event to the <em>57th General Conference</em> on Friday, 20 September. IAEA officials presented an information session concerning past and present RCF activities to current and potential members. The meeting also convened a panel of seven international experts for a round table discussion on nuclear regulatory cooperation between the RCF and Member States. </p>


